# 🚀 Dockerized Java Application

This is a simple Java program that prints the current date and time. The goal of this project is to practice Docker fundamentals by containerizing a basic Java application.

---

## 📌 Features

- ✅ Simple Java program to display current date and time
- 🐳 Dockerized using a custom Dockerfile
- 🛠️ Built and run inside a Docker container
- 🔁 Learned how rebuilding images is necessary after code changes

---

## 🧱 Tech Stack

- Java (JDK)
- Docker

---
